{"tid":1801323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請問泛民議員選舉後去曬邊?","createTime":"2019-12-28T14:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T15:02:31.000Z","uid":316329,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"12fc13d517fd951a682173566cfd05e8bea6b9ea","tid":1801323,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:07:12.000Z","msg":"泛民班律師見到法庭，黑警班走狗好似盲左咁?<br />\n<br />\n幾個月未試過去申請禁制令，私人告黑警?<br />\n<br />\n泛民又一年成功要我地含撚<br />\n<br />\n等睇泛民打手屌我分化撚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾會一票不投泛民</span></span>"},{"pid":"05c87d63eeb5e6797a0bd74f8c3edab43d2f47d5","tid":1801323,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#316329 - 你全家死了</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>正義女神蒙住對眼係咪為左縱容警暴&amp;藍絲? - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>屌你老母 <br />\n<br />\n正義女神蒙住對眼係咪就當睇唔到藍絲斬人，黑警殺人?<br />\n<br />\n人地打住法治旗號做緊政府隻走狗，你地傻仔就當法庭真係公正<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsosad.gif&h=5e5c7195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非幾時先識醒?</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1695144/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1695144/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>咪撚對前線警察郁手呀 !  屌你地老母咩 ! - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>大部分警隊前線警察, 佢地都係黃絲<br />\n包括司機, 同文職<br />\n做乜撚野要打佢地呀<br />\n係咪傻撚左呀<br />\n你怪佢地捉人?? 佢地係小薯黎咋,<br />\n就算唔驅散 拉人都好, 五大訴求都唔會理你,<br />\n分清目標啦 !!<br />\n唔好唔記得, 之前佢地都有警察, 曬委任證支持香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(但不包括速龍 果堆廢人)</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1621638/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1621638/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>以後有fa保護藍絲就請私了埋佢 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>懷疑共產黨已經成功混入左fa <br />\n<br />\n白衫比人圍緊就總有fa人牆保護，救人<br />\n<br />\n黑衫比藍絲同差佬打fa就每次消失曬<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fdead.gif&h=caf0bd2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底呢班fa係欺善怕惡定係共產黨派落黎扮同路人?</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1588868/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1588868/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>屌你老母消防狗又幫狗救熄路障 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>屌你老母班賤種太子站救人又唔見咁快手<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fdead.gif&h=caf0bd2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1571148/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1571148/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>泛民班垃圾律師去曬邊? - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>由6月到依家黑警放過期催淚彈，冇委任證，冇number <br />\n港鐵同機場都申請左幾次禁制令<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fdead.gif&h=caf0bd2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知泛民班垃圾係咪由6月開始比人送曬中?<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fdead.gif&h=caf0bd2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1549136/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1549136/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/AwtAz1F.png\" />"},{"pid":"67024234cb96591e3b74ee1d7f87d1827